description: How often have you sat down to a great meal only to be disappointed in your choice of beverage. Have you ever wondered what beer would pair nicely with tonight's meal. If so you no longer need to worry over these choices. Just ask "What beer?" and let "What beer?" help you complete that perfect meal. Please note that "What beer?" recommends alcoholic beverages, and as such may not be suitable for all ages, especially for those who are under the legal drinking limit in their country.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask what beer goes with a burger?
Alexa, ask what beer goes with fish?
Alexa, ask what beer goes with dessert?
name: What beer?
shortDescription: "What beer?" knows beer pairs well with your meal. Need some help deciding what to drink? Just ask "What Beer?". Not Suitable for those under the drinking age
